metadata.name: fRiENDSiES 1
metadata.description:
fRiENDSiES are your forever friend. Your new digital companion and inclusion into the kindness community aka the garden. This collection of 10,000 NFTs is made possible with love from FriendsWithYou.  
fRiENDSiES 00001 was our first bronze sculpture & interactive AR companion that also exists on the blockchain as an NFT. The artwork premiered at Soho Beach House during Art Basel Miami Beach 2021 and was auctioned by Christie's in collaboration with NFT Now.
